 is developing a <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../722/4288722.xml">
Reciprocating Chemical Muscle</link> for use in micro-scale flapping-wing aircraft. Michelson uses the term "entomopter" for this type of ornithopter. <institute wordnetid="108407330" confidence="0.8">
